text.tspan: In this phase a person does not consider his substance
abuse as problem. 50 – 60% of clients are in the stage of
Pre contemplation, which means they do not see a
problem and therefore they see no need to change their
behaviours. These include any client who is pressured or
coerced into services like AA or support groups.
